        {
            "title": "中國碳中和與陝西理穀新能源訂戰略合作",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國碳中和(01372)公布，與陝西理穀新能源簽署戰略合作協議，共同構建覆蓋綠氫生產、安全儲運、工業脫碳及綠色材料的全鏈條技術體系。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公告指出，陝西理穀新能源成立於2021年6月，專注於有機液體儲運氫成套技術及可再生能源技術開發與產業化應用，由國家級青年人才領銜，與華東理工大學開展深度產學研合作，擁有完全自主智慧財產權。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今次合作涉及綠氫生產與技術應用推廣等多個領域；中國碳中和董事會認為，合作契合本公司碳中和戰略佈局，有助強化公司在綠氫新能源產業及工業脫碳領域的技術與產業佈局，提升核心競爭力與可持續發展能力。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15846715-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%a2%b3%e4%b8%ad%e5%92%8c%e8%88%87%e9%99%9d%e8%a5%bf%e7%90%86%e7%a9%80%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e8%a8%82%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/01372-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 12:25:18",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "智譜正式發布GLM-5.1 據報再提價10%與海外頭部廠商價格對齊",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">智譜(02513)剛正式發佈GLM-5.1，據報智譜GLM已趁勢再提價10%，與海外頭部廠商價格對齊。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：智譜官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251211_FI_source-web_Zhipu-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：智譜官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251211_FI_source-web_Zhipu-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：智譜官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地媒體引述模型聚合平台OpenRouter的資料顯示，智譜GLM再提價10%後，GLM-5.1在Coding場景的緩存命中Token價格，已接近Anthropic旗下Claude Sonnet4.6水平，也是國產大模型首次在核心場景實現與海外頭部廠商的價格對齊。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道又指，國產大模型廠商在1年前尚需以降價90%以上爭奪市場佔有率，從今時今日智譜GLM開始與海外頭部廠商價格對齊，表明國產大模型不再單純依靠大幅降價爭奪市場，而是以性能溢價錨定國際基準。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">智譜今日再度顯著跑贏大市，股價半日漲14.06%，報888.5元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15846637-%e6%99%ba%e8%ad%9c%e6%ad%a3%e5%bc%8f%e7%99%bc%e5%b8%83glm-5-1-%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e5%86%8d%e6%8f%90%e5%83%b910%e8%88%87%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e9%a0%ad%e9%83%a8%e5%bb%a0%e5%95%86%e5%83%b9%e6%a0%bc%e5%b0%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/Zhipu-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 12:18:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市價量齊升 航空股乘勢炒上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中東戰火暫緩，帶動環球股市齊彈，內地股市今早裂口高開後亦穩步向上，滬深兩市半日交投已增至1.54萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指高開40點後反覆揚升，初段出現的半日低位3926點時仍漲36點或0.93%，早市大部分時間升幅維持在1%以上，尾市最高曾報3967點，升77點；滬指中午收報3964點，升74點或1.92%，成交6801.02億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指早市全程跑贏，初段最低13694點時升幅已達294點或2.2%，開市不足半小時升幅已擴大至約3%，其後持續穩步揚升，有逐漸向萬四點進發之勢；深指中午收報13919點，升518點或3.87%，成交8625.85億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也升122點或2.76%，收報4563點；創業板指數漲151點或4.81%，報3312點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：東航官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113943_source-web_00670東航-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東航官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-113943_source-web_00670東航-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：東航官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際期油價格大幅回落，油價成本有望回落亦成為航空股今早炒上的借口。東方航空(00670)A股(600115.SH)飆9.91%，報4.66元；南方航空(01055)A股(600029.SH)升7.49%，報6.03元；中國國航(00753)A股(601111.SH)也升6.57%，報7.14元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">有色金屬板塊同樣受捧，紫金礦業(02899)A股(601899.SH)升6.88%，報34.64元；洛陽鉬業(03993)A股(603993.SH)升8.01%，報19.01元；中國鋁業(02600)A股(601600.SH)漲7.55%，報12.25元；赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)升7.44%，報46.94元；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升6.68%，報42.35元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15846524-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%83%b9%e9%87%8f%e9%bd%8a%e5%8d%87-%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e8%82%a1%e4%b9%98%e5%8b%a2%e7%82%92%e4%b8%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 11:40:20",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新西蘭央行維持利率2.25厘不變 警告通脹壓力增強或需加息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新西蘭央行宣布維持指標利率不變，基準利率保持在2.25厘，符合市場預期。不過，央行在聲明中釋放鷹派信號，暗示若通脹壓力進一步加劇，已做好採取行動的準備。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">數據顯示，新西蘭目前通脹率為3.1%，已超出央行設定的1.0%至3.0%目標區間。隨著中東地緣政治危機推高燃料及運輸成本，市場預計通脹率將會進一步攀升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">央行預計今年通脹率將上升至4.0%以上，近期整體通脹的具體升幅，將視乎中東衝突的演變，以及全球供應鏈與能源市場受幹擾的程度及持續時間。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">央行聲明指出，今次決定維持利率不變，已平衡了針對中期通脹上升風險採取預防措施的潛在收益，以及避免因不必要地抑制經濟復蘇而付出的代價，又強調將致力確保通脹在中期內回歸至2.0%水平。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15846456-%e6%96%b0%e8%a5%bf%e8%98%ad%e5%a4%ae%e8%a1%8c%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%81%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%872-25%e5%8e%98%e4%b8%8d%e8%ae%8a-%e8%ad%a6%e5%91%8a%e9%80%9a%e8%84%b9%e5%a3%93%e5%8a%9b%e5%a2%9e%e5%bc%b7%e6%88%96",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20231003_FI_source-web_NZ.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 11:33:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股半日收漲2649點或4.96%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股今早大幅高開後持續在高位徘徊，日經平均指數半日漲2649點或4.96%，報56078點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15846249-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e6%bc%b22649%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%964-96",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/AP26098072533459.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 10:50:20",
